    {
      "Text": "This update for dnsmasq fixes the following issues\n\nUpdate to 2.93:\n\n- CVE-2026-12725: heap buffer overflow in `log_query()` when logging unsupported DS/DNSKEY replies (bsc#1268764).\n",
